<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<style>
  .body { font-family: 'Helvetica', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 20px; }
  .card { max-width: 500px; background: #ffffff; margin: 0 auto; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
  .header { background-color: #4b5563; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
  .content { padding: 30px; text-align: center; color: #1f2937; line-height: 1.6; }
  .footer { font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; text-align: center; padding: 20px; }
  .btn { background: #3b82f6; color: #ffffff; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block; font-weight: bold; }
</style>
</head>
<body class="body">
  <div class="card">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="{{logoUrl}}" width="100" alt="{{company}} Logo">
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2 style="color: #111827;">Account Deactivated</h2>
      <p>Hi {{firstName}},</p>
      <p>This is a confirmation that your account at <strong>{{company}}</strong> has been successfully deactivated.</p>
      <p>Your data is preserved, but you will no longer receive notifications or be visible to other users. You can return at any time by logging back in.</p>
      <br>
      <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="btn">Reactivate My Account</a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">© {{year}} {{company}} | Privacy Policy</div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
